title: Google\Cloud\Asset\V1\BigQueryDestination
name: BigQueryDestination
description:
A BigQuery destination for exporting assets to.

Generated from protobuf message google.cloud.asset.v1.BigQueryDestination

Extends Google\Protobuf\Internal\Message

params.name: data
params.description: Optional. Data for populating the Message object.

params.name: data.dataset
params.description: Required. The BigQuery dataset in format "projects/projectId/datasets/datasetId", to which the snapshot result should be exported. If this dataset does not exist, the export call returns an INVALID_ARGUMENT error.

params.name: data.table
params.description: Required. The BigQuery table to which the snapshot result should be written. If this table does not exist, a new table with the given name will be created.

params.name: data.force
params.description: If the destination table already exists and this flag is TRUE, the table will be overwritten by the contents of assets snapshot. If the flag is FALSE or unset and the destination table already exists, the export call returns an INVALID_ARGUMEMT error.
